I have produced an example implementation in this branch;

[https://bitbucket.org/JonathanWheare/vrx/branch/topic\_namespace\_generation](https://bitbucket.org/JonathanWheare/vrx/branch/topic_namespace_generation)

This adds three namespaces to the wamv model, corresponding to the vehicles thrusters, sensors and the cameras.  Using this, the following topic organisation;

![](data/bitbucket.org/repo/BgXLzgM/images/2745955233-vrx_topics.png)
Becomes this;

![](data/bitbucket.org/repo/BgXLzgM/images/1164964962-vrx_topics_revised.png)
Since the thrusters and some sensors are named by their position on the vehicle, this reorganisation would group related topics together.  This type based organisation should improve clarity when reviewing the vehicles topics.

Regards,

Jonathan.
